{"type":"message","id":"00ef3a9a","parentId":"0f16b9cf","timestamp":"2026-04-01T11:49:53.284Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Done. I've successfully completed the autonomous learning task by:\n1. Checking for active sessions - none found (only the cron task itself)\n2. Searching for latest trends in three key areas related to 道简网络's business\n3. Compiling and saving a comprehensive learning note with 4 key insights\n\nLet me provide a brief summary to the user.","thinkingSignature":"14cc5a9234d212a13ab1dc4c4938438b0a7bf108dc8e3e8e1e244f2ae81ef546"},{"type":"text","text":"<final>\n已完成自主学习任务，无活跃对话（仅当前cron任务运行）。\n\n**学习成果已保存至** `memory/学习笔记.md`\n\n---\n\n**3条关键行业洞察摘要：**\n\n1. **企业数字化** — 2026年政策驱动强劲，国产化从\"鼓励\"升为\"全栈强制\"，AI多智能体（70%企业部署）和垂直领域大模型成主流，数据要素成为核心生产要素\n\n2. **智能安防/弱电** — AIoT+边缘计算驱动系统从\"被动响应\"升级为\"主动预判\"；数字孪生大型项目普及率超60%；行业从工程交付向服务化运营转型\n\n3. **IT运维** — AI Agent替代脚本化自动化，\"自主运维\"试点落地；外包从\"全面接管\"升级为\"智能共营\"，外包商向\"战略顾问\"演进\n\n**对道简网络战略启示**：三重机遇叠加（政策补贴最高5000万 + 国产化强制要求 + AI落地爆发），To B科技服务商处于重要战略窗口期。\n</final>"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":4985,"output":303,"cacheRead":43981,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":49269,"cost":{"input":0.0014954999999999999,"output":0.0003636,"cacheRead":0.00131943,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0031785299999999997}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775044184483}}
